# MyPiTrade

MyPiTrade is a mobile-friendly frontend application for testing Pi Network integrations in **sandbox mode**.

## Features
- Sandbox mode enabled for safe testing
- Mobile-friendly interface
- Connects to your Pi account without real transactions
- Simple and clean UI

## Setup Instructions

1. **Clone this repository**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<username>/MyPiTrade.git
